(This ain’t just a funny video, ladies. )
Let me say this loud and clear!
some of y’all really have girlfriends… and still have the nerve to be in my DMs like I’m blind, stupid, or desperate. I could expose everything ,and trust me, I’ve got the receipts. Screenshots. Voice notes. Videos. Your girlfriend’s Instagram? Yeah, I got that too. But up until now, I’ve kept it respectful, because I don’t like to ruin lives or bring drama.
But if y’all keep crossing the line, I will speak up. I will post it. And I will expose everything. Not for attention , but because I’m done being disrespected like I don’t have boundaries. You think I’m quiet because I’m scared? No baby, I’m quiet because I’ve been protecting people who didn’t deserve it.
This is your first and final warning. If you’ve got a girl, stay loyal to her. If you’re just out here being messy for fun ,go somewhere else. Stop testing people’s patience and pretending like your actions have no consequences.
What am I to you? A secret? A plaything? A joke? I’m not one of them. I’m not built for your fantasy, I’m built for respect. Next time y’all slide into my DMs acting bold, just know: I’m one post away from turning your whole situation upside down.
And to the queens out there ,I may not know you personally, but I’m always standing with you. Wake up. Check your man. Protect your heart. You deserve better.

latestPosts.caption:
Today is not just Sunday… it’s the day my Savior rose ✨. The stone was rolled away, and with it, every weight, every fear, every shame that tried to hold me down.
This is the day LOVE stood up and said, “Death, you don’t win.”
Jesus didn’t just walk out of that tomb for Himself,He walked out with me on His mind, and you in His heart ❤️.
He saw every broken part of me and still chose the cross ✝️. He knew the cost and still said, “You’re worth it.”
Nothing stopped Him not the betrayal, not the pain, not even the grave. He rose so we could rise too
And guess what? The devil LOST ❌
Hell is defeated. I can step on the devil’s head with boldness ️🦶🔥
He’s under my feet, full of shame, while I walk in victory like the child of God I am 👑
Easter is the loudest “I love you” the world has ever known 💌
So today, I smile through the tears 🥹 because I know I am loved, chosen, forgiven, and free.
He is alive and because He lives, I can face tomorrow ☀️
Happy Resurrection Sunday ✨
My heart is full. My soul is grateful. My joy is real. Thank You, love you Jesus. You did it all 🙌
#heisrisen #thankyoujesus #easterjoy #jesuslives #faithoverfear #lovewin #rubenraj
